a hit-and-run accident.

04:32.373 --> 04:34.742
The incident occurred at 1400.

04:34.808 --> 04:40.080
The victim was a white female,
approximately 30 years old.

04:40.147 --> 04:45.252
The vehicle which struck her
was a black Chevrolet cargo van.

04:45.353 --> 04:49.790
